      "title": "He and Charan: He is also Charan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Another person has surrendered to the Karuwathota police on charges of trespassing into the Sri Lanka Rupavahini Corporation and disrupting the programme.",
        "Samintha Kelumpriya Amarasinghe (age 45) has surrendered. He is the second person to enter the Rupavahini Corporation.",
        "Meanwhile, actor Jehan Abuhami, who entered the President's palace, surrendered at the Fort Magistrate's Court. The court has released him on bail."
      ],
